Akaọrụ - Ọkaiwu

Eze nwaanyị kacha maa mma na Naịjirịa n'afọ 2013
Ezinne Akudo Anyaoha (amuru 17 Mee 1990)  bu onye okaiwu Naijiria na eze nwanyi mara mma
Akudo amuru na Imo State

Ọ gụchara akwụkwọ na mahadum Federal Government Girls' College, Owerri Imo State, wee nweta akara ugo mmụta iwu na Abia State University, mechaa mechaa ụlọ ọrụ National Youth Service Corp na steeti Ogun
N'afọ 2013, Akudo meriri asọmpi ịma mma Miss Nigeria
N'afọ 2015, Akudo bidoro ọrụ ya dịka ọkaiwu
ma guzobe ụlọ ọrụ nke na-ahụ maka igbochi idakpo mmadụ n'ike site na otu ya na-abụghị nke gọọmentị; Ụlọ ọrụ a  dị na Lagos, Nigeria
Ọ na-agbasikwa mbọ ike n'itinye ọnụ ya megide inwe mmekọ n'ike
Na 2018, a họpụtara Akudo dị ka onye isi ekere uche nke Miss Nigeria Pageant
